This is a simple script lets you flash a message on the document page title.

It is best to only call the flasher when page is not visible. See the following gist
for a simple Page Visiblity Polyfill for jQuery (it adds $.visibilityState).

https://gist.github.com/1604828



Note, this code is place up in jQuery ($.doc_title_flasher) for namespace purposes. 